{"tid":2314374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[兒時回憶問題]幼稚園有冇默書？","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T16:47:10.000Z","uid":237438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d84df14cfdc26a7e109ed9f3788049b0a520789c","tid":2314374,"uid":237438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩食飯同老婆屋企人討論到一人個問題。就係我話宜加幼稚園制度唔比兒童咁辛苦唔會有默書。我老婆就話冇可能點會宜加比已前容易，佢細個幼稚園冇默書。但係我記憶入邊我幼稚園係有默書（我91年出世）。<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">請問大家記唔記得已前幼稚園有冇默書?</span></span>"},{"pid":"d179a9bcb1f3ee7b54d69307282d75eefdde658b","tid":2314374,"uid":380973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"我記得有排隊出去串英文，串岩就可以去玩，串錯要排隊再串過，默書好似又真係冇 （93）"},{"pid":"49aca309cbf1f62f73f47da92119ee956d28222e","tid":2314374,"uid":237438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d179a9bcb1f3ee7b54d69307282d75eefdde658b","tid":2314374,"uid":380973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"我記得有排隊出去串英文，串岩就可以去玩，串錯要排隊再串過，默書好似又真係冇 （93）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"thanks"},{"pid":"57649ebd96d5c0116f284d81a3c1c90e66bcc8cd","tid":2314374,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"4a06b4f878506b88b30744d406cac96f27d7a9e1","tid":2314374,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"022fc708b65d9ecf5e2958888d3a16cdb3e27982","tid":2314374,"uid":237438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a06b4f878506b88b30744d406cac96f27d7a9e1","tid":2314374,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"問個問題姐😅"},{"pid":"3b6fc5cd29ef5ed829a485c180861562379e58a1","tid":2314374,"uid":368454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-0