ormal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"印象中第一次串錯嘅字就係brother，串咗borther"},{"pid":"70a1a98b15c174ffa784c06d712dcfac93166164","tid":2314374,"uid":102189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"記得有考試問我用英文講屋企電話"},{"pid":"24a3782fdf869e826c8e58c4a160bc9c195dbdb6","tid":2314374,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T16:47:10.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n試過出貓比老師鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}